data.description: Discover the charm of Historical College Park, a pedestrian-friendly neighborhood just 5 minutes from the Airport and 6 miles from the heart of downtown Atlanta. This area boasts popular dining and nightlife options, all within a comfortable walking distance. Don't miss your chance to see this stunning property today, conveniently located just moments from the prestigious Woodward Academy! Featuring an open floor plan, this home provides ample space for its residents, including 4 large bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. The house is bathed in natural light thanks to oversized windows, and the interior design maximizes functionality in every corner. Enjoy designer lighting throughout the home, and as an added highlight, there's a custom-built wet bar. Two decks, equipped with ceiling fans, offer additional outdoor living space. The expansive master bedroom comes with a newly renovated, spa-like master bathroom. Upstairs, find two more bedrooms, while the basement level houses an additional bedroom and a playroom.
